1
00:00:53,080 --> 00:00:54,000
I bet they’re having a one-night stand right now.

2
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:57,080
If I don’t get any good sleep,
don’t you dare dream of going to heaven!

3
00:00:57,080 --> 00:00:58,480
I'll show you!

4
00:00:58,480 --> 00:00:59,920
Your stuff is a total mess.

5
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:00,600
Clean it up, will you?

6
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:03,600
Chai, you jerk! You were doing it so loudly,
how was I supposed to sleep?

7
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:05,800
Oh my god!

8
00:01:05,800 --> 00:01:08,160
I am the "President of this Village," okay?

9
00:01:08,160 --> 00:01:08,920
You never clean the house!

10
00:01:08,920 --> 00:01:10,360
This place is messy, dirty, and disgusting!

11
00:01:10,360 --> 00:01:13,400
What about you?
You bring both men and women over to do it at this house!

12
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:15,520
If you’re so annoyed by me, then just move out!

13
00:01:15,520 --> 00:01:17,200
I’m not leaving!

14
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:17,840
You have to leave!

15
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:18,600
No, YOU leave!

16
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:18,920
- You leave!
- You leave!

17
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:20,240
- You leave!
- You leave!

18
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:29,320
Finally, some downtime!

19
00:01:29,320 --> 00:01:31,440
Ms. Petchgam Ploy let us work...

20
00:01:31,440 --> 00:01:33,160
like slaves...

21
00:01:33,160 --> 00:01:36,040
Oh, quit whining!

22
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:40,040
I'll do anything for First Class.

23
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:42,200
Harder!

24
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:45,280
Copy that, Ms. Fertilizer brand shirt.

25
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:48,520
Jeez, Chaba! Why are you just taking it?

26
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:51,720
You’ve got zero dignity left.

27
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:54,160
Dignity? Chaba’s dignity?

28
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:58,120
That died the same day as my Ga-be Ga-be bag.

29
00:01:58,120 --> 00:02:00,520
She tried to act all "healthy lifestyle,"

30
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:02,400
then took my bag on a run!

31
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:04,720
And do you know what kind of run it was?

32
00:02:04,720 --> 00:02:07,320
The Color Run India!

33
00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:11,320
My bag literally came back looking like a rainbow.

34
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:15,360
You took an Indian's rainbow bag for a jog?

35
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:20,560
Gift, you’re hallucinating. Go to bed.

36
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:22,480
Yeah...

37
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:25,400
And since she’s too broke to pay me back for the bag,

38
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:27,520
she’s stuck being a servant till this day.

39
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:29,520
Time for some hermit yoga stretches...

40
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:39,320
Let’s sleep. Let's be considerate of the others.

41
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:41,360
I was just getting comfortable.

42
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,360
C'mon.

43
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:44,200
Come on, get over here.

44
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:47,040
Ugh, you idiot!

45
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,360
A soft bed feels like heaven, doesn't it?

46
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:55,360
Seriously. I missed this kind of bed so much.

47
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:03,640
Gift, do you have a dog at home?

48
00:03:03,640 --> 00:03:05,640
Who is a good boy?

49
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:10,120
Gift!

50
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,760
With those shaky breaths?
That's definitely not a dog.

51
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:13,480
I bet they’re having a one-night stand right now.

52
00:03:13,480 --> 00:03:15,400
Damn it, it’s like this every single night.

53
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:18,560
I told him "don't do it, don't do it,"
but he keeps going for it anyway!

54
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:20,320
"Dog, dog, dog..."

55
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:23,160
"Have you ever seen a doggie?"

56
00:03:23,160 --> 00:03:26,200
Oh, keep it down!

57
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:27,880
For god's sake, what kind of dog is that?

58
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:29,200
"He’s got ears, he's got eyes..."

59
00:03:29,200 --> 00:03:33,200
"And a long tail..."

60
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:36,680
I said shut up!

61
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:42,080
Gift, don't you dare let them win!

62
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:46,440
If I don’t get any good sleep,
don’t you dare dream of going to heaven!

63
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:47,840
That's right!

64
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:55,720
Harder! Give it to me harder!

65
00:03:57,400 --> 00:04:00,720
It’s so big and so long!

66
00:04:00,720 --> 00:04:04,720
This feels so good!

67
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:16,360
Hey, it’s working!

68
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,360
Alright, let’s go to sleep.

69
00:04:21,960 --> 00:04:23,960
Chaba and I didn't do a thing.

70
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:25,000
It was all Gift.

71
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,960
Doing all that "Ooh-ooh, Aah-aah" or whatever.

72
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:28,800
Why’d you stop?

73
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:29,920
Keep moaning!

74
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:30,920
The guy likes it.

75
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:35,600
Keep going! Make it loud!

76
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:39,720
Fine, I’ll give it to 'em.

77
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:51,440
They're feeling it every second.

78
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:52,920
Okay, this doesn't feel right anymore.

79
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:54,320
Then try mine.

80
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:59,680
Chakangrao Grass Jelly!
Chakangrao Grass Jelly is here!

81
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:03,680
For anyone who’s never seen a grass jelly plant...

82
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,200
Wait, is the grass jelly working for them too?

83
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:07,200
Let me handle this.

84
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,400
Chaba!

85
00:05:17,400 --> 00:05:19,200
I can't take this anymore.

86
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:21,120
Nothing about this is normal.

87
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:23,040
The longer we stay, the more haunted this place gets.

88
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,760
Hey, let’s just go sleep at our places.

89
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:25,760
Gift, you stay here and sleep alone.

90
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:26,720
Yeah, you stay right here.

91
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,520
You’re just gonna ditch me like that?

92
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:31,080
I know your house is all fancy but I’m outta here.

93
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:37,720
Chai, jerk, I'm sleepy!

94
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:39,720
Am I ever gonna get any sleep tonight?

95
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:55,240
What the hell is this?

96
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:58,400
Tid-Gift, your stuff is making this place a total mess.

97
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:00,360
I don't even have a spot to rest my big toe.

98
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:02,360
Clean this up.

99
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,360
Smartass.

100
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:08,000
Tid-Gift!

101
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,000
Wake up!

102
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:13,520
Hey!

103
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:16,200
Are you seriously sleeping right now?

104
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:19,200
Sleeping with your eyes open?
That’s advanced. Looking cool as hell.

105
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:32,560
Hey, wake up!

106
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:34,560
Tid-Gift! Tid-Gift!

107
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:41,240
Your stuff is a total mess.
Clean it up, will you?

108
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:43,040
Can I do it later?

109
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:45,000
Hey, get up! Get up, get up, get up!

110
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:47,760
Ugh, Chai! Get up for what?

111
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:51,120
Last night you were doing it so loud
the sound reached the end of the alley!

112
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,680
Who could even sleep through that?

113
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:54,120
Have some sympathy, will you?

114
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:56,520
Get up, Tid-Gift! Get up!

115
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:58,520
Chai, I’m not getting up. I’m sleepy.

116
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:05,920
You get up! Get up right now!

117
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:07,560
I've got a cramp in my leg, Tid-Gift!

118
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:09,120
You get up! Get up right now!

119
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:12,160
I've got a cramp in my leg, Tid-Gift!

120
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,240
Chai, get up!

121
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,240
I told you, I can't move!

122
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:19,240
Ah! Broad daylight and already a love scene?

123
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,240
Oh my god! A ghost!

124
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:23,160
Me?

125
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:26,000
Oh, dear. I'm not a ghost.

126
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:28,000
Just a beautiful lady.

127
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:33,520
Who the hell are you, old lady?

128
00:07:33,520 --> 00:07:36,800
Ouch! You two are so harsh.

129
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,200
Old lady, my ass.

130
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:39,720
Call me Big Sis.

131
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,240
My name is...

132
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:45,040
Priscilla.

133
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:45,920
Whoa.

134
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,760
My name is Priscilla, sweeties.

135
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:49,160
It's Priscilla.

136
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:51,280
It’s like this, darling. Originally...

137
00:07:51,280 --> 00:07:53,560
My old name was "Lah."

138
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:55,000
Have you seen the drama "Lah"?

139
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,000
Are you even old enough?

140
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:58,040
My mother loved that show.

141
00:07:58,040 --> 00:08:00,480
She was obsessed with it.

142
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:03,440
So she named me Lah.

143
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:10,360
But you can just call me Priscilla.

144
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:13,160
See? Even my backstory is entertaining.

145
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:22,160
But anyway, I am the headman of this village.

146
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,720
The headman of this village?

147
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:26,520
And that gives you the right to just walk into anyone's house?

148
00:08:26,520 --> 00:08:29,680
Oh, darling. When new residents move in...

149
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,760
I have to keep an eye on things and look after you.

150
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:33,760
By the way, do you have a dog?

151
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:40,160
And do you guys screw often?

152
00:08:40,160 --> 00:08:44,160
When you do, is it all loud like...

153
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:47,520
We aren't husband and wife!

154
00:08:47,520 --> 00:08:51,520
Geez. Okay then, don't mind me asking...

155
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:53,640
But can I have the Wi-Fi password?

156
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:03,200
Thanks, sweetie!

157
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:05,600
Wow, this internet is fast.

158
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,040
Fabulous!

159
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:08,360
Sweetie, sweetie...

160
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:10,360
don't take this the wrong way...

161
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:12,560
but why is your house so messy?

162
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:16,480
In this day and age,
women shouldn't have to sit around doing housework.

163
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:19,600
My husband never makes me do a single chore.

164
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,760
Don't let them win, darling.

165
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:23,960
What era is this?
Everyone is equal now.

166
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:26,320
That’s true.

167
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:28,360
It’s 2026 already.

168
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:32,360
The era of Thai male supremacy is over.

169
00:09:32,680 --> 00:09:35,120
It’s not about equality!

170
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:38,120
It’s about YOU. You! You!

171
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,480
You’re just gross and filthy.

172
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:42,440
Do you really think you can fly First Class living like this?

173
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:45,400
Hey, Chai. What if Ms. Petchgam Ploy finds out...

174
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:49,400
that yesterday you had a "secret snack"
with a First Class passenger on the Brazil flight?

175
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:50,800
Do you think they’ll still hire you?

176
00:09:50,800 --> 00:09:53,200
Are you gonna report me?

177
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:55,560
You, Tid-Gift! You...

178
00:09:55,560 --> 00:09:57,160
Hello? What's up?

179
00:09:57,160 --> 00:09:59,760
Yeah, girl. I'm at the new neighbors' house.

180
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:02,400
Chai, why wouldn't I do it?

181
00:10:02,400 --> 00:10:03,360
You, Tid-Gift! You...

182
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:06,200
Bitch, are you for real? For real again?

183
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:11,200
Bitch, are you for real?

184
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:15,200
Old lady! Get lost and talk somewhere else.

185
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:17,520
Does that mean you're going out, darling?

186
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:19,280
I'll watch the house for you.

187
00:10:19,280 --> 00:10:20,120
I mean YOU.

188
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:20,720
Please leave.

189
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:22,040
Please.

190
00:10:22,040 --> 00:10:23,280
You mean me?

191
00:10:23,280 --> 00:10:24,440
You!

192
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:26,480
Alright then. I won't disturb you.

193
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:30,480
Thanks for the Wi-Fi password!

194
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:35,440
That way.

195
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:36,840
This is the bedroom, right?

196
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:39,840
Duh!

197
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,040
Darling...

198
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:43,840
Where is the exit?

199
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:45,720
Leave the same way you came in!

200
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:47,120
Please escort yourself out!

201
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:48,680
See you later!

202
00:10:48,680 --> 00:10:49,680
Fabulous!

203
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:56,720
That damn ghost lady.

204
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:57,400
Tid-Gift!

205
00:10:57,400 --> 00:10:57,880
Chai!

206
00:10:57,880 --> 00:10:58,640
Clean this up.

207
00:10:58,640 --> 00:10:59,400
I’m not doing it.

208
00:10:59,400 --> 00:11:00,040
You do it!

209
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:01,040
I’m gonna sleep.

210
00:11:01,040 --> 00:11:03,120
Sleep my ass! Clean this up!

211
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,120
Get up and clean it, Gift!

212
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:18,400
Chaba, dear, take off the glasses.

213
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:20,400
I'm not wearing any.

214
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:21,400
I mean my glasses, dear.

215
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:28,160
And the mirror.

216
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:30,160
And lipstick shade 009, too.

217
00:11:32,280 --> 00:11:33,280
Thank you.

218
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:35,960
Do you need me to apply it for you?

219
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:39,120
No need, dear.

220
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:42,480
But could you please massage my pinky?

221
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:44,960
It’s a bit stiff.

222
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:45,960
Why don't you massage it yourself?

223
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:50,240
What did you say?

224
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:52,240
I said, why don't you massage it yourself?

225
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:59,920
Chaba, dear...about that Ga-be Ga-be bag.

226
00:11:59,920 --> 00:12:03,920
My mom bought that for me
when I passed the flight attendant exam.

227
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:08,400
But you went and stained it.

228
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:10,200
I'm sorry, Sky.

229
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,800
It’s okay, Chaba.

230
00:12:11,800 --> 00:12:15,800
I know you probably can't afford to buy me a new one.

231
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:18,480
Since all your money...

232
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:20,320
goes into your beauty treatments.

233
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:22,200
And weight loss.

234
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,680
That’s why I have you...

235
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:25,880
serving me like this.

236
00:12:25,880 --> 00:12:28,440
I only do it because you’re my friend.

237
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:30,560
This is out of the kindness of my heart.

238
00:12:30,560 --> 00:12:33,160
Sky, you’re so good to me.

239
00:12:33,160 --> 00:12:37,160
Of course, because we’re friends forever.

240
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,280
Chaba...

241
00:12:39,280 --> 00:12:39,960
Yeah?

242
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:43,320
Could you go buy me a ceremonial grade matcha?

243
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:44,320
Just one cup.

244
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:49,160
Do you still think I'm that stupid? Huh?

245
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:50,880
Let me tell you something.

246
00:12:50,880 --> 00:12:51,480
What?

247
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:54,120
That bag of yours...

248
00:12:54,120 --> 00:12:56,240
I took it to a bag spa.

249
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:57,840
And do you know what they told me?

250
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:58,480
What?

251
00:12:58,480 --> 00:13:00,840
They said it’s a fake. A complete knock-off!

252
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:04,280
Nonsense! That shop must be clueless.

253
00:13:04,280 --> 00:13:07,720
They aren't clueless.
They said a girl with a pockmarked face walked in...

254
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:10,720
took it to the bag spa, and they told her it’s 100% fake.

255
00:13:13,760 --> 00:13:16,240
Chaba...

256
00:13:16,240 --> 00:13:18,920
Even if the bag is fake...

257
00:13:18,920 --> 00:13:22,440
my kindness for you...

258
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:24,440
is the real deal.

259
00:13:28,280 --> 00:13:30,080
Cut it out, Sky.

260
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:31,840
You’re even faker than that bag.

261
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:33,360
Let me tell you something.

262
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:36,720
"Mutta is no longer your victim.

263
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:38,240
And neither is Chaba."

264
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:40,320
Mark my words. From now on...

265
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:42,000
"Independence"...

266
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:45,320
isn't just a road name.

267
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:46,560
