539
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:16,120
The power went out at my place.

540
00:27:16,120 --> 00:27:19,800
I just wanted to find a place to charge my phone.

541
00:27:19,800 --> 00:27:20,960
So you brought this extension cord here?

542
00:27:20,960 --> 00:27:21,840
Yeah.

543
00:27:21,840 --> 00:27:23,120
And used it to tie us up?

544
00:27:23,120 --> 00:27:25,480
Well, yeah...and...

545
00:27:25,480 --> 00:27:27,040
Auntie?

546
00:27:27,040 --> 00:27:29,320
Call me Big Sis.
Try calling me that!

547
00:27:29,320 --> 00:27:31,320
Auntie!

548
00:27:31,320 --> 00:27:32,960
Ugh, you old hag!

549
00:27:32,960 --> 00:27:34,400
Shut up!

550
00:27:34,400 --> 00:27:35,400
Fine.

551
00:27:35,400 --> 00:27:36,400
As for you...

552
00:27:36,400 --> 00:27:37,600
where's the watch?

553
00:27:37,600 --> 00:27:39,520
Go back up and get that watch.

554
00:27:39,520 --> 00:27:41,520
