562
00:28:07,800 --> 00:28:10,720
I think I’m having diarrhea!

563
00:28:10,720 --> 00:28:12,400
Hey! Don't you dare poop here!

564
00:28:12,400 --> 00:28:13,440
You'd better shut up!

565
00:28:13,440 --> 00:28:14,360
We're gonna die covered in shit!

566
00:28:14,360 --> 00:28:15,360
