567
00:28:22,720 --> 00:28:23,720
Chai!

568
00:28:25,280 --> 00:28:26,280
That was a terrible angle for a fall.

569
00:28:27,680 --> 00:28:28,680
Chai!

570
00:28:28,880 --> 00:28:30,440
Chai, wake up!

571
00:28:30,440 --> 00:28:31,440
Don't you die on me!

572
00:28:31,440 --> 00:28:33,560
Why are you being like this?

573
00:28:33,560 --> 00:28:35,000
I'm so sorry!

574
00:28:35,000 --> 00:28:36,400
When I said you weren't important...

575
00:28:36,400 --> 00:28:37,920
the truth is, you mean everything to me!

576
00:28:37,920 --> 00:28:39,920
You’re so important to me!

577
00:28:41,400 --> 00:28:42,360
Chai, please wake up!

578
00:28:42,360 --> 00:28:42,840
I...I...

579
00:28:42,840 --> 00:28:44,440
It’s okay.

580
00:28:44,440 --> 00:28:45,560
Chai!

581
00:28:45,560 --> 00:28:47,200
I have one request.

582
00:28:47,200 --> 00:28:50,160
Please serve real fish maw soup at the funeral.

583
00:28:50,160 --> 00:28:52,840
Ugh, what's with all the drama?

584
00:28:52,840 --> 00:28:55,480
It’s a fake gun!

585
00:28:55,480 --> 00:28:59,480
Wait, if that wasn't a gunshot...then...

586
00:28:59,520 --> 00:29:00,800
That was my fart.

587
00:29:00,800 --> 00:29:03,080
What?

588
00:29:03,080 --> 00:29:05,440
I’ve got gas.

589
00:29:05,440 --> 00:29:09,440
I’ve been eating clean, so the gas just keeps coming, man.

590
00:29:09,720 --> 00:29:10,720
Hey!

591
00:29:11,160 --> 00:29:12,160
Hey!

592
00:29:14,120 --> 00:29:15,120
Now’s our chance!

593
00:29:18,800 --> 00:29:22,760
Gotcha, gotcha, Chai!

594
00:29:22,760 --> 00:29:25,520
You think you’re tough?
You can’t take me down!

595
00:29:25,520 --> 00:29:26,120
Hey!

596
00:29:26,120 --> 00:29:26,880
Sky!

597
00:29:26,880 --> 00:29:27,800
Who the hell are you?

598
00:29:27,800 --> 00:29:28,800
Sky!

599
00:29:36,840 --> 00:29:38,920
Before I became a queen,

600
00:29:38,920 --> 00:29:40,920
I was a freaking gangster!

601
00:29:49,320 --> 00:29:52,080
Finally finished cleaning up.

602
00:29:52,080 --> 00:29:54,080
Take your stuff upstairs, too.

603
00:29:59,320 --> 00:30:04,920
What you said earlier...about being afraid of losing me...
did you mean it?

604
00:30:04,920 --> 00:30:08,960
When I said you weren't important...
the truth is, you mean everything to me!

605
00:30:10,080 --> 00:30:12,560
