606
00:30:14,680 --> 00:30:17,680
Right...are you sure?

607
00:30:17,680 --> 00:30:21,680
I just thought you were gonna drop dead,
and I didn't want to clean up your corpse.

608
00:30:23,120 --> 00:30:24,120
That’s touching.

609
00:30:25,280 --> 00:30:26,280
You really want to die, don't you?

610
00:30:36,320 --> 00:30:38,400
At this very second...

611
00:30:38,400 --> 00:30:42,400
Neither of them can hold back anymore.

612
00:30:43,040 --> 00:30:45,560
Yearning to belong to one another...

613
00:30:49,760 --> 00:30:50,760
Auntie!

614
00:30:52,560 --> 00:30:54,600
You scared the hell out of me!

615
00:30:54,600 --> 00:30:58,600
Don't mind me.

616
00:30:58,600 --> 00:31:01,200
The power is out at my place and the internet is terrible.

617
00:31:01,200 --> 00:31:02,800
I’m hooked on this Chinese drama.

618
00:31:02,800 --> 00:31:05,680
So I’m just borrowing your Wi-Fi and electricity.

619
00:31:05,680 --> 00:31:08,840
I won't be a bother, though.
I brought my own power strip.

620
00:31:08,840 --> 00:31:09,360
Auntie.

621
