624
00:31:14,080 --> 00:31:15,440
Can I?

625
00:31:15,440 --> 00:31:16,440
No!

626
00:31:17,600 --> 00:31:19,000
Do you even realize what you're doing?

627
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:21,760
Stirring up trouble and making everyone fight...
is it that much fun for you?

628
00:31:21,760 --> 00:31:24,040
No, honestly.

629
00:31:24,040 --> 00:31:28,040
I just want everyone to be harmonious and get along.

630
00:31:28,240 --> 00:31:30,640
When we have grudges in our hearts...

631
00:31:30,640 --> 00:31:34,120
