632
00:31:34,120 --> 00:31:35,720
You have to talk to each other.

633
00:31:35,720 --> 00:31:36,960
But...

634
00:31:36,960 --> 00:31:38,160
it’s actually a good thing.

635
00:31:38,160 --> 00:31:39,360
If you're still fighting like this,

636
00:31:39,360 --> 00:31:40,920
it means you still love each other.

637
00:31:40,920 --> 00:31:42,440
And with all this bickering...

638
00:31:42,440 --> 00:31:46,080
the old folks say it’s a guarantee...

639
00:31:46,080 --> 00:31:48,960
you’re gonna have a dozen kids!

640
00:31:48,960 --> 00:31:50,960
We aren't husband and wife!

641
00:31:52,520 --> 00:31:54,400
Well, whether you are or not, I wouldn't know.

642
00:31:54,400 --> 00:31:55,680
If you'll excuse me...

643
00:31:55,680 --> 00:31:57,120
