644
00:31:57,120 --> 00:32:02,640
The internet is fast, and the power is on.
I think I'll finish my drama right here.

645
00:32:02,640 --> 00:32:05,640
I'm going to bed, Auntie.
Turn off the lights when you're done.

646
00:32:13,560 --> 00:32:14,040
That’s it!

647
00:32:14,040 --> 00:32:17,360
Hey, Chai! You’re disgusting.
What are you doing down here?

648
00:32:17,360 --> 00:32:19,320
If you’re gonna jerk off, go do it upstairs!

649
00:32:19,320 --> 00:32:21,120
What the hell are you talking about?

650
00:32:21,120 --> 00:32:22,840
