651
00:32:22,840 --> 00:32:24,880
If I don't move, it's gonna fall.

652
00:32:24,880 --> 00:32:25,560
Oh...

653
00:32:25,560 --> 00:32:28,000
Damn it! I lost.

654
00:32:28,000 --> 00:32:29,000
That's on you, Tid-Gift.

655
00:32:29,200 --> 00:32:31,800
I thought you were jerking off.

656
00:32:32,200 --> 00:32:34,680
Hey, what kind of thoughts are those?

657
00:32:34,680 --> 00:32:36,360
What are you thinking, huh?

658
00:32:36,360 --> 00:32:38,120
What?

659
00:32:38,120 --> 00:32:41,400
What are you...

660
00:32:41,400 --> 00:32:42,600
hiding behind your back?

661
00:32:42,600 --> 00:32:43,240
Nothing.

662
00:32:43,240 --> 00:32:44,320
Are you stealing my stuff?

663
00:32:44,320 --> 00:32:46,120
No! My butt was itchy.
I was just scratching it.

664
00:32:46,120 --> 00:32:48,680
Just scratching my butt, that’s all.

665
00:32:48,680 --> 00:32:51,120
Seriously, nothing!

666
00:32:51,120 --> 00:32:55,120
Hey, what's this?

667
00:32:56,640 --> 00:32:57,640
This is for you.

668
00:33:02,360 --> 00:33:03,360
