669
00:33:05,120 --> 00:33:09,120
How cute...a matching "husband and wife" toothbrush set.

670
00:33:09,600 --> 00:33:12,600
Bitch, they're different colors so we don't mix them up!

671
00:33:15,720 --> 00:33:19,280
Well, thanks.
Anyway, come here, come here...

672
00:33:19,280 --> 00:33:21,280
