677
00:33:41,320 --> 00:33:43,720
Chai! You’re disgusting! That’s filthy!

678
00:33:43,720 --> 00:33:46,280
What do you mean, filthy? You wanna fight?

679
00:33:46,280 --> 00:33:48,840
