680
00:33:48,840 --> 00:33:49,840
You want a piece of me?

681
00:33:49,840 --> 00:33:50,840
Huh? You want a piece of me?

682
00:33:50,840 --> 00:33:52,200
So? What's it gonna be?

683
00:33:52,200 --> 00:33:54,680
You're not done? Stop!

684
00:33:54,680 --> 00:33:55,840
Stop it! You want some?

685
00:33:55,840 --> 00:33:58,280
You want some, huh?

686
00:33:58,280 --> 00:34:00,280
Wait and see! Ewww!

687
00:34:03,920 --> 00:34:05,880
Try and dodge this!
Don't let it touch you!

688
00:34:11,720 --> 00:34:12,960
Wait for the cue!

689
00:34:12,960 --> 00:34:15,120
Man, that scared the crap out of me.

690
00:34:15,120 --> 00:34:16,120
I'm still massaging my face.

691
00:34:21,360 --> 00:34:23,040
Hey, what's this paper?

692
00:34:23,040 --> 00:34:25,240
