746
00:36:18,400 --> 00:36:20,200
London, baby!

747
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:22,720
Emperor, what are you holding?

748
00:36:22,720 --> 00:36:23,320
It's a sperm...

749
00:36:23,320 --> 00:36:24,160
What?

750
00:36:24,160 --> 00:36:26,040
of Norwegian Salmon.

751
00:36:26,040 --> 00:36:29,560
Today, our cabin crew will demonstrate a Special Edition safety briefing!
